<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

  <h2>What to have ready</h2>
  <p>Before your appointment, it helps to have the following to hand:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A list of your current medications (or bring the packets with you)</li>
    <li>A brief description of your symptoms and when they started</li>
    <li>Any previous test results or hospital letters relevant to your visit</li>
    <li>Questions you'd like to ask — writing them down helps you remember</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Telephone consultations</h2>
  <p>Many appointments are carried out by telephone. To get the most from a phone consultation:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The clinician will call you at the agreed time — please keep your phone on and nearby</li>
    <li>Find a quiet, private space where you can talk comfortably</li>
    <li>Have a pen and paper ready in case you need to note anything down</li>
    <li>The call is private and confidential</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If the clinician needs to examine you, they will arrange a face-to-face follow-up.</p>

  <h2>NearMe video consultations</h2>
  <p>If a clinician invites you to a video consultation, you can join at <a href="https://nhsattend.vc/scoonie-medical-practice" rel="noopener noreferrer">nhsattend.vc/scoonie-medical-practice</a>. No account or app is needed.</p>
  <p>To prepare:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Use the latest version of Safari, Chrome, or Edge</li>
    <li>Check your camera and microphone are working</li>
    <li>Find a well-lit room with a good internet connection</li>
    <li>Only use NearMe when a clinician has invited you — it is not a walk-in service</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>One problem per consultation</h2>
  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 not-prose">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark"><strong>For your safety</strong>, we prefer to deal with one problem per 10-minute consultation. If you have more than one issue, please let us know when booking so we can allocate more time or arrange a second appointment.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>If you can't make it</h2>
  <p>Please let us know as soon as possible if you cannot attend your appointment, so we can offer the slot to another patient. Call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>.</p>

</div>
